ing: 2 fresh jalapeno peppers, seeded and chopped
des: "This is a wonderful spicy coleslaw recipe for pot luck or bbq's. I always get asked for this recipe."
ins: In a large bowl, toss together the coleslaw mix, corn, Cheddar cheese, jalapeno and cilantro. In a separate bowl, stir together the Ranch-style dressing, cumin, coriander, garlic powder and lime juice. Pour over the coleslaw mixture, and toss to coat. Serve right away, or refrigerate until serving.
